title: Earthquake deformation field for Haiti earthquake 12 January 2010
name: Earthquake deformation field for Haiti earthquake 12 January 2010
description: The Okada deformation model has been applied to the USGS Finite Fault Model (http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eqinthenews/2010/us2010rja6/finite_fault.php) to obtain the vertical displacement. Values are in meter
